Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so here we are in\N好的，现在我们来到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the final of the Solution Videos\N挑战自适应布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Adeptly Adaptive Challenge,\N系列的最后部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are two things we need to accomplish here.\N这有两个事情需要我们去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Each news item should be 200 X 275 in narrow state,\N每一个新的元素在窄状态时，宽高为200*275
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and 400 X 400 tall when in a wide state.\N同时在宽状态时，宽高为400*400
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we're defining the wide state\N这里给我们宽状态的定义是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as 900 min window width.\N窗口宽度大于等于900px
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In the narrow state, the Headline should be 18 point,\N在窄状态，这标题应当是18pt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and 26 point in the wide state.\N在宽状态应该是26pt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then also we're going to hide the AutoSuggestBox\N同时我们还要在宽度小于等于400px的压缩状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,when in a narrow state of 400 or less.\N隐藏自动提示框
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so this will apply really\N好，这个效果仅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,only to the MainPage.xaml.\N用于MainPage.xaml
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This will only apply to our User Control that we created The NewsItemControl..\N这个仅用于我们创造的用户控制 NewsItemControl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go ahead and get started here,\N然后我们从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:01:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and let's open up the NewsItemControl.\N打开 NewsItemControl
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And inside of our Grid,\N在我们的Grid布局中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,right after the Grid.RowDefinitions, we're going to\N在Grid.RowDefinitions下面，我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,start adding a VisualStateManager,\N开始添加一个视觉状态管理器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,creating the VisualState groups,\N创建视觉状态组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll create one VisualState group.\N我们要创建一个视觉状态组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And inside that we'll create two VisualStates.\N在这里我们要创建两个视觉状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one I'm going to call the NarrowLayout,\N第一个我们叫做窄布局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing on keyboard)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the second one\N然后是第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call WideLayout.\N我叫他宽布局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it really matters,\N其他它并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're not referencing it by name.\N因为我们不会通过名字来引用它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But any rate, okay,\N不管怎样，好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then, here we go, VisualState.StateTriggers,\N然后，这里添加，VisualState.StateTriggers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then VisualState.Setters.\N然后是 VisualState.Setters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll just copy and paste that here as well.\N我再复制再粘贴一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so in the Triggers, I'm going to\N在这个触发器中，我将要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,create an AdaptiveTrigger where\N创建一个 AdaptiveTrigger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the MinWindowWidth\N设置窄布局的最小窗口宽度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,will be "0" for the NarrowLayout.\N为0
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll make this MinwindowWidth\N然后我们设置宽布局的最小窗口宽度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"900" in the WideLayout.\N为900
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And remember this is really on a per app basis.\N这种设置实际上基于于每个应用的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever makes sense for your application,\N只要在你的应用中合理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,where the logical breaks are.\N符合逻辑即可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no like as I've said many times already,\N就像我之间反复提及过的，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no standard way to do this that I'm aware of.\N做这玩意没有一个标准的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be corrected as some point here, but...\N这儿可能我需要修改一些地方，但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to set that MainPanel.Width,\N我们设置 MainPanel.Width,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and let's make sure that we have\N然后将它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that's called MainPanel here.\N命名为MainPanel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I want to call this...\N这里我想给它起个名字...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this Name...MainPanel.\N就叫....MainPanel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? So we're going to set...\N好了，我们还要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing on keyboard)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the MainPanel's Width to a value of 200.\N把MainPanel的宽度设为200
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And the MainPanel.Height\N然后是MainPanel的高度
