Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(takes a deep breath)\N(深呼吸)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the other requirement was\N然后其他的要求是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to...\N去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)\N(打字中……)
