Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.\N让我们开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, it did not like that.\N这不像刚刚那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\N噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)\N(打字中……)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be right, yeah. It just didn't like that.\N这就好了，不像刚刚那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good alright, so then we'll change\N好了，没问题了，然后我们要改变
