Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so in this case we want 400 X 400,\N我们想要设置为400*400
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and...\N然后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll set this Font at 26.\N我们把字体设为26
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that should complete the first of the two... items.\N这样我们应该完成了这两个中的前一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go over to the MainPage.xaml,\N现在让我们跳转到MainPage.xaml
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to need to add\N我们需要去添加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a VisualStateManager.\N一个视觉状态管理器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, let me just do this.\N这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I hate typing all this stuff out.\N因为我讨厌把这些东西都敲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just grab all this, we'll strip out the stuff we don't need.\N选择这些东西，然后去掉我们不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we'll just get rid of these Setters,\N好的，让我们去掉这些Setter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think the MinWindowWidth is going to be 400, any rate.\N我认为这个最小窗口宽度应该是400，任何比例的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(sighing)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so in this case what we're going to do\N现在我们要做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is set the MyAutoSuggestBox.Visibility\N设置 MyAutoSuggestBox 的可见性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll set that equal to Collapsed.\N我们把他设为Collapsed（收缩的）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll do the same here,\N然后在这里做同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(typing)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and it should be set to Visible,\N它应该被设为Visible（可见的）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe is the property there.\N我相信是这个属性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's save it, and let's see what we got.\N好了，让我们保存一下，看看我们得到了什么
