Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now unfortunately\N好吧，现在不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't really go smaller than 400.\N我们不可以缩小到400
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I can't, so to test this,\N至少我不行，所以让我们来测试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're going to do...\N我要做的是..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is change to the Mobile Emulator.\N切换到手机模拟器
